text: Before I Self Destruct is 50 Cent's fourth album. It was released in 2009.Jokesta (June 26, 2007]). 50 Cent Adds to Curtis, Rumored Promo Campaign Begins For Eminem's upcoming LP . Def Sounds. Accessed July 21, 2007.
